title: J.R.R. Tolkien - Complete Works
description:
This pdf contains all the known works of J.R.R. Tolkien, a biography and various notes. Books included in this file (and their authors) include:

<list>The Silmarillion (J.R.R. Tolkien)
The Hobbit (J.R.R. Tolkien)
The Fellowship of the Ring (J.R.R. Tolkien)
The Two Towers (J.R.R. Tolkien)
The Return of the King (J.R.R. Tolkien)
J.R.R. Tolkien: A Biographical Sketch (David Doughan)
Forword to The Silmarillion (Christopher Tolkien)
Forword to The Hobbit (J.R.R. Tolkien)
Maps of Middle Earth (J.R.R. Tolkien, Christopher Tolkien and others)</list>
